MEGCoordinateSystemDescription: Coordinates system used to index voxels in the space of the MRI volume, in millimeters. Axis X: left>right. Axis Y: posterior>anterior. Axis Z: bottom>top. Coordinates of the first voxel at the bottom-left-posterior of the MRI volume: (1,1,1). http://neuroimage.usc.edu/brainstorm/CoordinateSystems
